	"keywords": "React Native, Android, Android App Development",
	"description": "I recently switched jobs, and one of my first tasks was to create a bottom sheet\nin React Native. \n\nComing from a native Android development [https://ayusch.com/] background, I\nthought it was going to be as daunting as creating a bottom sheet in native. But\nI was so wrong! I was so mesmerized that I decided to write a simple tutorial on\ncreating a bottom sheet in React Native.\n\nA bottom sheet is a useful component that slides up from the bottom of the\nscreen and often contains different options.",
	"headline": "Why I Switched to React Native to Create a Super Easy Bottom Sheet",
	"author": {
